# Comprehensive Testing Strategy - 2025

Complete testing pyramid implementation with Vitest/Jest for unit tests, integration tests with mocked dependencies, and Playwright for E2E testing.

**Justification:** Multi-layered testing prevents regressions, ensures reliability, validates business logic, and maintains confidence in production deployments.

## 🎯 Single Responsibility
This rule defines testing standards, patterns, and coverage requirements. It does NOT cover CI/CD integration (see ci-pipeline) or deployment validation (see deployment-stages).

## 📋 Master Testing Checklist

### Project Setup
```markdown
- [ ] Choose test framework (Vitest for new, Jest for existing)
- [ ] Configure test runners and environments
- [ ] Set up coverage thresholds (80% global, 70% per-file)
- [ ] Configure test directories structure
- [ ] Set up test data factories
- [ ] Configure mocking strategies
- [ ] Set up E2E test infrastructure
- [ ] Configure mutation testing (Stryker)
- [ ] Set up visual regression testing
- [ ] Configure performance testing
```

